<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/playground.css">
    <title>Playground</title>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>
    <h1>Playground</h1>
    <div id="canvas"></div>
    <div id="player-editor" ></div>
    <button id="run-button" @click="onClick">Run!</button>
    <h2>Methods</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>player.moveUp() ：プレイヤを上に移動</li>
        <li>player.moveTo(position) ：プレイヤを指定した場所(bottom，center，top)へ移動</li>
        <li>player.moveDown() ：プレイヤを下に移動</li>
        <li>player.randomMove() ：プレイヤを上か下にランダムに移動</li>
        <li>player.shot() ：攻撃</li>
        <li>player.randomAttack() ：プレイヤがランダムに上下に動きながら攻撃</li>
        <li>player.upDownAttack() ：プレイヤがtop->bottom->tom->...と動いて攻撃</li>
    </ul>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/ace/1.2.0/ace.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/p5@1.0.0/lib/p5.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/vue/dist/vue.js"></script>
    <!-- <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/vue"></script> -->
    <script src="/js/utils/character.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/render.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>